<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Karell</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-08-29 19:22:05</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>After camping the Lava Elemental on and off for a week or so to get my Monk a pendant, (leaving when EXP groups want it, or sharing when someone wants to share), I got the pendant on my 14th Lava Elemental. He spawns about 1/4 or 1/5 of the time, and after killing I guess about 50 or so Gnome clockworks, I'm still only dubious. I did kill Gabbie a few times too though, and I would guess that her faction hits are heavier than the regulars. Anyway, 3K is a breeze compared to camping that dang thing. The common drops (Inferno Damage Shield potions) are good for low level twinks, but that's about it. I'd pay maybe 4K for one, know that I know the length of the camp.<BR>
<BR>
Total camp time? 20 hours, one pendant, 13 potions. Is 4Kpp worth 20 hours of game time? Of course it is.</font></td></tr></table>
